data.description: Looking for an immaculate retreat? Look no further! With the oversized screen porch, gourmet kitchen, private owner's suite, and oh, so much more, this is the place for you.        Nestled in a private cul-de-sac, just a stone's throw from all conveniences, you'll love the privacy.  And, with it being in a swim, tennis community, entertainment abounds.  Escape to your own oasis of tranquility nestled in quaint Madison, GA. Welcome to your dream home, where every detail has been crafted for comfort and enjoyment.     As you step through the front door, you're greeted by an inviting atmosphere that whispers of serenity. The oversized screen porch beckons you to unwind with a good book or sip your morning coffee in peace, surrounded by your private retreat.      Inside, the gourmet kitchen awaits, a culinary haven where masterpieces are born, and relationships are forged through intimate gatherings, celebrations and simple family meals. With its open layout and cozy breakfast area, it's the perfect spot for gathering with loved ones and creating lasting memories.        For more formal occasions, the elegant dining room offers the ideal setting. And when it's time to retire for the night, the owner's suite on the main level provides a luxurious sanctuary where you can escape the cares of the day.    Upstairs, three additional bedrooms await, offering the perfect space for family and guests. One of these bedrooms even boasts its own private bath, ensuring comfort and convenience for everyone.         Outside, the house sits in a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering a sense of privacy and seclusion. And as part of a vibrant swim/tennis community, you'll have access to amenities that make every day feel like a vacation.        But perhaps the best part of all is the location. Just a stone's throw from shopping, schools, and all the conveniences of modern life, yet still a world away from the hustle and bustle. And with Hard Labor Creek State Park, Athens and Lake Oconee just a short drive away, you'll have endless opportunities for adventure and exploration.        So come, experience the rest and relaxation you deserve at this exquisite home in Madison, GA. Your oasis awaits.
